content:
I apologize for any confusion. After reviewing the information, it seems that I made a mistake in my previous response.

To clarify, Joseph Miller was the son of Mary F. Price and Joseph Samuels Miller. He was not directly related to Eliza Gardner, who was the daughter of Marie Therese Raison de la Geneste Gardner and Joseph Gardner.

Thank you for bringing this to my attention, and I apologize for any confusion my previous response may have caused.
